1 A BILL for an Act to amend and reenact subsection 2 of section 4.1-01-27 of the North Dakota
2 Century Code, relating to the agriculture infrastructure grant program.
3 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
4 SECTION 1. AMENDMENT. Subsection 2 of section 4.1-01-27 of the North Dakota Century
5 Code is amended and reenacted as follows:
6 2. The agriculture commissioner, in consultation with the director of the department of
7 transportation, shall award grants to political subdivisionsa county, township, or city
8 with a population of one thousand five hundred residents or less, for road and bridge
9 improvements necessary to accommodate value-added agriculture businesses. Grant
10 funding under this subsection may be used for:
11 a. Corridor improvements on city, county, and township roadways; and
12 b. Improvements to roads or bridges that provide access to value-added agriculture
13 businesses.
